{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-numbers-61-to-100/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Vežbovao sam izgovor brojeva od 60 do 69.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-numbers-61-to-100","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U prethodnom dijelu, naučili ste o broju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sesenta</span> (60) na španskom jeziku.</p>\n<p>Sada ćeš naučiti brojeve od 61 do 69.</p>\n<p>Ovi brojevi su formirani korišćenjem reči trideset <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sesenta</span> (60), praćeno spajanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> (\"i\"), i ciframa jedinica (1-9).</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Nambari</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kihispania</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">60</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">61</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">62</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">63</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">64</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">65</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">66</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">67</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">68</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sesenta y ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">69<